dc_title_s: Calhoun County, Iowa, 1973, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol 19025. Form of individual image numbering: 19025-473-[number], or 19025-573-[number]. Year flown 1973. Flown by Air Tech Inc. Scale, 1:20,000|Contact the Map Collection at The University of Iowa Libraries: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact/|Scanned at 300 ppi in Greyscale.
